---
// Seção final de conversão antes do footer
---

<section
  id="candidatura"
  class="section-py relative overflow-hidden"
  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251,190,10,0.06) 0%, var(--mb-black) 50%, rgba(251,190,10,0.03) 100%);"
  aria-labelledby="cta-heading"
>
  <!-- Linhas decorativas -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-mb-yellow/20 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-mb-border to-transparent"></div>

  <!-- Glow central -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 50%, rgba(251,190,10,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="container relative z-10 text-center">

    <!-- Eyebrow -->
    <p class="eyebrow mb-6" data-animate>Pronto para fazer parte?</p>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2
      id="cta-heading"
      class="section-title max-w-3xl mx-auto text-balance mb-6"
      data-animate
      data-animate-delay="100"
    >
      Tava faltando você
      <span class="text-mb-yellow"> nessa conversa.</span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Subtítulo -->
    <p
      class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10"
      data-animate
      data-animate-delay="200"
    >
      Sente aqui com a gente. O Masterboard existe para provocar com cuidado,
      acolher com exigência e elevar líderes que ainda estão construindo.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA principal -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center"
      data-animate
      data-animate-delay="300"
    >
      <button
        type="button"
        class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4"
        data-open-modal
        aria-label="Iniciar processo de candidatura ao Masterboard"
      >
        Faça parte do club
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Microcopy de confiança -->
    <p class="text-white/30 text-sm mt-6" data-animate data-animate-delay="350">
      Acesso por curadoria para proteger quem está dentro.
    </p>

    <!-- Logos / certificações (placeholder) -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-6 mt-12 pt-10 border-t border-mb-border"
      data-animate
      data-animate-delay="400"
      aria-label="Informações de membros"
    >
      {[
        { number: '800+', label: 'membros ativos' },
        { number: '1.200+', label: 'encontros realizados' },
        { number: '12+', label: 'cidades' },
        { number: 'R$5bi+', label: 'faturamento combinado' },
      ].map(({ number, label }) => (
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-white font-800 text-xl md:text-2xl" style="letter-spacing: -0.03em;">{number}</p>
          <p class="text-white/35 text-xs">{label}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
